# openhands-preview-test.demorec
# Simple terminal-only demo for testing OpenHands primitives in preview
Output openhands-preview-test.mp4
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720

@mode terminal:openhands
rows 30
theme "Dracula"
---

# Show initial state
Type "echo 'Testing OpenHands CLI Primitives'"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

# Install OpenHands CLI
Install

# Note: Start, Prompt, WaitForReady, Quit require actual OpenHands CLI
# and LLM configuration to work. For preview testing, Install is sufficient
# to demonstrate the primitive expansion.

Type "echo 'OpenHands CLI installed successfully'"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "which openhands"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
